content.text: Welcome to our Temporal Discounting Experiment!

This screen is followed by a brief survey. 
We encourage you to fill it in as accurately as possible.

The survey is followed by 72 trials. In each trial, 
you will be presented a choice between $20 now, and
an amount at a delayed time. 
Further instructions are provided before the trials!

Press Enter to Continue

8.content:
Identifier (name/username/faceroll)

Age

What is your current level of study?

Roughly what percentage of your monthly expenses are on:

Essentials (Rent, Food, Tech etc.)

Leisure (Outings, Movies, Books, etc.)

Investments (Savings, Bonds, Crypto, etc.)

On a scale of 1-6 (6: breaking down/on the verge)
How stressed are you feeling?

On a scale of 1-6 (6: dreams are coming true!)
How happy are you feeling today?

How many hours of sleep did you get last night?
8.title: Form

content.text:
Press Enter to Continue
Please download your data from the link at the end of
program and send it across to us!
Option 1 is always the same: $20 now

Press the '1' key to select $20 now, 
OR
'2' key to select the displayed alternate

You have 10 seconds to make a choice
There is a half second gap between trials,
and a fixation cross for 1 second at the start of each trial

Press Enter when you're ready to begin!
